  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub, not your words. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A year-round election-analysis platform built on atomic data units (candidates, races, precincts), spun out of EJ's NBC Big Board work. It shipped alongside two open-source helpers: <code class=\"md-inline-code\">election-helpers</code> (npm) and an election-data-generator (Observable).</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Precinct-level election results as an interactive choropleth\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/electology/map.png\" alt=\"Precinct-level election results as an interactive choropleth\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/electology/map.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/electology/map.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/electology/map.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/electology/map.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Precinct-level election results as an interactive choropleth\" width=\"2396\" height=\"2262\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.1deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2396×2262\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-square w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"election-helpers — open-source election data tooling\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/electology/helpers.png\" alt=\"election-helpers — open-source election data tooling\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/electology/helpers.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary